ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectConvention for the avoidance of Double Taxation and the Prevention of Fiscal Evasion with respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital (Luxembourg)
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate powers to sign, on behalf of Canada, subject to ratification, (1) the PROTOCOL amending THE CONVENTION between Canada and the GOVERNMENT OF THE GRAND DUCHY OF LUXEMBOURG for the AVOIDANCE OF DOUBLE TAXATION AND THE PREVENTION OF FISCAL EVASION WITH RESPECT TO TAXES ON INCOME AND ON CAPITAL; and (2) the EXCHANGE OF NOTES concerning the Convention.
